name: yellow bike, 5x7 print
description:
this image is a classic, with it's saturated yellow and deep depth of field, everyone stops and looks closer when they see it. i live with a bike collector, his bikes are always in some new project and undergoing a transformation and the yellow one has always stayed his classic bike.

this image was taken with a vintage yashica 35mm camera. it is professionally printed on archival kodak endura paper with a lustre finish. it will be signed by the artist and has a small white border, perfect for framing.

all items are wrapped carefully and beautifully because packages at your door are special.
